author: mikedd
msg: OPENJPA-632 porting svn rev 584463 to 1.0.x. The overridden toSelect() signature in the OracleDictionary was no longer appropriate since the DBDictionary.toSelect() change in revision #577972 (which fixed OPENJPA-378). This resulted in the special Oracle range handing to no longer take place, resulting in setFirstResult() and setMaxResults() effectively being ignored for Oracle.
